  ✓ Sell apps built with AppLib                — ALLOWED (free)
  ✓ Modify AppLib for your app                 — ALLOWED (share mods)
  ✓ Create plugins/themes/extensions           — ALLOWED (free)
  ✓ Create complementary tools                 — ALLOWED (free)
  ✓ Contribute to AppLib                       — ALLOWED & WELCOME
  ✓ Use internally without distribution        — ALLOWED (free)
  
  ✗ Create competing UI framework              — NOT ALLOWED
  ✗ Fork and create "BetterLib"                — NOT ALLOWED  
  ✗ Offer AppLib as a service                  — NOT ALLOWED

